          ToggleButton.sideToolbarToggle.tipsToggle:checked:pointerover /template/ ContentPresenter#PART_ContentPresenter,
          ToggleButton.sideToolbarToggle.tipsToggle:checked:pressed /template/ ContentPresenter#PART_ContentPresenter">
